data.description: LOOKING FOR A HOME THAT HAS IT ALL? WELL THIS IS IT. CALL TO PREVIEW THIS NEAT & CLEAN, MOVE IN READY CBS POOL HOME CONVENIENTLY LOCATED IN THE NORTH POINTE COMMUNITY JUST A SHORT DISTANCE FROM BEAUTIFUL BOK TOWER GARDENS. IF YOU WANT LOW POWER BILLS, THIS HOME HAS IT WITH SOLAR PANELS (WHICH ARE PAID FOR) SO THERE IS ALMOST NO ELECTRIC BILL. THIS 3 BEDROOM 2 BATH POOL HOME COMES WITH A LIVING/DINING ROOM COMBO, A FLORIDA ROOM OVERLOOKING THE SCREEN ENCLOSED POOL. SPLIT FLOORPLAN. INSIDE UTILITY ROOM. A 2 CAR GARAGE AND COMES WITH HURRICANE SHUTTERS FOR THE WINDOWS. AND AS A SPECIAL FEATURE FOR THE MAN OF HOUSE, MIKE'S MAN SHED, A GREAT LITTLE GET AWAY. ALL THIS AND PRICED TO SELL.
